{"TopicId":156174,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Larger launch pad mod?","CreatedByName":"spec111","CreatedById":174739,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-08T19:43:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"spec111","CreatedById":174739,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-08T19:43:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello! I need larger launch pad to launch my 86000t missile! =) It is crashing over bumpy surface every time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Streetwind","CreatedById":98962,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-09T08:38:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know of any such mod, but as a workaround, have you tried loading the vehicle into the spaceplane hangar and putting it onto the runway? That one at least has more space in two out of four directions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-09T10:31:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstall this mod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/151818-12x-kerbal-konstructs-0989-12122016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand mod(s) listed in its \u0022\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003ESupported Contend-Mods:\u003C/span\u003E\u0022 section. (Kerbin-Side, etc).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the right-down corner of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E view this will add a button of launchpad selector.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-09T10:33:07Z\u0022 title=\u002202/09/2017 10:33  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}